## Allgemeine Referenzen

### Database Schema (master-context.md Zeile 57-114)
- products: id, name, category, quantity
- employees: id, name, position, email, start_date, monthly_salary
- work_hours: id, employee_id, date, hours
- customers: id, name, email, phone, address
- orders: id, customer_id, order_date, status
- order_items: id, order_id, product_id, quantity

### Folder Structure (master-context.md Zeile 117-150)
```
backend/
  server.js, db.js, package.json
  routes/ (inventory.js, hr.js, sales.js, analytics.js)
frontend/
  *.html, css/style.css, js/*.js
contexts/
  master-context.md, project-status.md, CONTEXT-LOADER.md
  phases 8-10/ (Phase-8/9/10-spec.md)
archive/
  Phase1-7/ (historische Dokumentation)
```

---

## Kontext-Optimierung

| Situation | Empfehlung |
|-----------|------------|
| Neues Feature | Nur relevante Spec + Template-Code laden |
| Bug Fix | Betroffene Datei + Tests laden |
| Refactoring | master-context.md fuer Architektur |
| QA Review | project-status.md + relevante Spec |

**Ziel**: Fokussierter Kontext (~500 Zeilen) statt vollstaendiger Dump (~3000+ Zeilen)
